Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,170)\fn\fs30}Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(227,287)}Sangetsu Bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(399,111)}Welcome to\NSangetsu Bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First you skip out on your trip,\Nthen you stay out all night, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going on the graduation trip
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave your "school mood" behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your job interview?\NMy senior there was pissed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't in an accident or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better retreat fast. If Asako\Nfinds you, she'll chew you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,404)}Episode 4:\NReal Reality, Fabricated Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's seriously inconvenient having no memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did I kill 20,000 NEETs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I don't have a clear grasp\Nof what happened to them afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that I gathered\N20,000 NEETs here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yes.\N--For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I really did do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And why was I chosen to be a Selecao, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say. I haven't been\Ninformed of the selection criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you haven't been informed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Correct.\N--What's the "Supporter" then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supporter is one of the twelve Selecao,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and is a system responsible for\Neliminating those unfit to be saviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, it's pointless to ask you about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who should I ask?!\NTry putting yourself in my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that guy\Ntold me to ask the other Selecao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308,214)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(409,383)}[Pay respects to the Social\Ninsurance Office's medical\Nclaim inspector]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(431,403)}[The Alumnl Association's\Nentertainment of a technical\NOfficer]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? He's practically\Ngot something going every minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is Number 5 just asking\Nyou to do things all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when we get complex requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we divide them into several steps\Nand carry them out separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So this all stems from one request?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(312,218)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(321,342)}[Pay respects to the Social\Ninsurance Office's medical\Nclaim inspector]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(315,348)}[The Alumni Association's\Nentertainment of a technical\NOfficer]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Juiz, would you find out who\Nhad an MRI machine delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(316,348)}[Donation to the Solitary\NPeople's Party Policy\NThink Tank]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,352)\fn\fs18}[Tickets to a party in\Nsupport of Dr. Hiroto\NShoda]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,two days ago from Toyo Medical Tech?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(318,351)}[Gift to Akihiro Ogawa's\Nelection campaign\NHeadquarters]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(317,349)}[Tickets to a party for\NAssemblyman Takumi\NSanada]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(319,340)}[Entertain members of the\NRatings Committee]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(314,340)}[Soji Univ. Alumni Association\N(Gunma Chapter) Special\NGeneral Meeting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(314,351)}[Gift to Shinichi Koyanagi's\Nelection campaign\Nheadquarters]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepted. I pray you shall\Ncontinue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(316,351)}[Call on Seiji Murata to\Nrun for mayor, plus\Ncampaign funds]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222,109)}Exit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(329,65)}Exit Here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,96)}Road Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The missile landing site...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, couldn't he see the sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was just gonna\Nfling his bike off the edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like in that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old young-adult movie where\Nhe flings his scooter in the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the title of that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody watches young-adult movies these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johnny! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Quadrophenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the title of the movie\Nyou were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quadrophenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me in with that guy.\NI'm not particularly in despair right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get to the Kan-Etsu Expressway, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And it seems like it was this\Nmorning before she finally got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Apparently she stayed\Nover at Micchon's last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki! Osugi's on the phone for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so worried, he called over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hello.\N--Sorry, were you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Sorry I didn't contact you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just happy you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you stay over at Micchon's last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So, what happened with your interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They let me reschedule for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have prospective employee\Ntraining starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But isn't this out of your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! Interviews make\Nyou feel really alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to be brave with someone else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Micchon's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(201,298)}[I went home this morning\Nwithout saying anything,\Nbut did something happen\Nto you?! I hope your memories\Njust came back, but I got a\Nlittle worried, so I'm texting\NYou. Reply when you have time.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(239,259)}[Message Sent]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,143)}Hiura General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I believe someone at this hospital\Nbought an "MRI machine" yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an odd question...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to venture a guess,\NI'd say perhaps the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. In that case, sorry to trouble you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but could you tell the director I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon? I'm sorry, but do you\Nhave an appointment...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I think he'll see me if\Nyou tell him a Selecao is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like there's only old people around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317,171)}Literary Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220,84)}"Unknown Source of Funding"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(479,197)\fn\fs22}"Hospital Director Hajime Hiura\NPurchased a Bankrupt Regional Hospital"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs22\pos(279,197)}"Rumors of Rampant\N Bribery in the\N Prefectural Assembly"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to read this trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To us, Dr. Hiura is a savior.\NNo matter what anybody says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,206)}[Saki Morimi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki Morimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18}[Incoming Call: Blocked Number]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be the one calling himself a Selecao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, my name is Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I found out where the MRI\Nmachine in your log was delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... What number are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pardon?\N--What number Selecao are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so Number 9 is the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute. That Kondou\Nguy said the same thing to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And would "Kondou" refer to Number 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we talk face to face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently I erased my own memory,\Nand I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not about this phone, or Selecao,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or this "game" we're supposedly playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd just like you to tell me about it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you killing me,if that's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not inclined to be\Nkilled while I still have money left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it's fine. I'll have\Nsomeone bring you medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take it, you should find out\Nhow you got that cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is the medicine, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast! So I don't have\Ntime to think about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of doctor poisons\Nsomeone in a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,jeez, he's some doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day. This is Mr. Outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting on my own highly personal convictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to peremptorily\Nselect twelve saviors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to save this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am calling those twelve the Selecao,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have appointed one\Nof them as the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, you are a Selecao.\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the Supporter is what\Nyou could call the "Twelfth Man":
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a fanatic supporter of the team\Nas well as a cold-hearted watchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be aware that if you do not\Nfunction correctly as a Selecao,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be judged harshly by the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not the Supporter, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I know which of the twelve is the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be you, or it might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the twelve, they are people I recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to have strongly wished to be Selecao,\Nwhether they realized it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you will not be\Nallowed to refuse this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone I've given you\Ncontains ten billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave its use entirely to your discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to lead this\Ncountry in the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,using whatever ideas you may have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this ten billion\Ncannot be converted to cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you have any requests,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a concierge is available to assist you at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if you push the center button on your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The cost of these requests will be\Ndeducted from your ten billion yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and other Selecao will be\Nnotified of your usage history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, let me tell you\Nabout the penalties involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be aware that Selecao who\Nmeet the following conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,will meet a swift and sure death\Nat the hands of the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First: Those who seek to abandon\Ntheir mission and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Second: Those who go a long period\Nof time without using their phone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and achieve no results.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Third: Those who exhibit a\Npattern of using the ten billion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,fortheir own personal desires\Ninstead of in the national interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth: Those whose balance reaches\Nzero before they've saved the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this list is by no means exhaustive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like all chosen ones to take the\Nutmost responsibility for their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, only the first Selecao\Nto accomplish the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will ultimately survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as someone crosses the finish line,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the remaining Selecao will\Nbe automatically eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? So just\Ngetting chosen is a penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be all from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you successfully find a\Nway to save this country
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and cross the finish line first, you will\Nautomatically be brought to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Noblesse oblige. I sincerely\Npray you shall be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it like this foryou when you\Ngot your phone, too, Mr. Hiura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it was a little theatrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I wanted to live\Nto see my request granted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,at today's Prefectural Assembly meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I put you to sleep, in case\Nyou were the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What I showed you should\Nbe more or less correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That day I stumbled into a taxi drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next thing I knew, I was\Ncovered in vomit facing a strange box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to reproduce the vomit part...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you know what he meant when\Nhe said you wanted to play this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in a way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd felt the limitations of myself\Nas a brain surgeon for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, one doctor can only\Nsave so many people in his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered patients in this neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the same time had\Ntheir families move here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and had the law changed\Nso that we could hire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the elderly this country\Nwas on the verge of abandoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and used my ten billion\Nto create a private hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where we could hire them as manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if I can just get the local\Ngovernment to run this system,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my work will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(249,132)}[Developnment of\Nreganative medicine in\Nthe medico-industrial city]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(271,204)\fn\fs18}[Establish a\Nmedico-industrial fund]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(294,290)}[Biotechnology research\Nand personnel\Ndevelopment center]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Were all of your purchases bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Juiz is brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In this short span of time,\Nshe's won over the entire Assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Juiz did? Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So does this mean that I\Nand the other Selecao will die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just my personal\Nideal hospital, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it impresses Mr. Outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If this isn't enough to win, what the\Nhell else would you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That Outside guy is a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, he seems more like a generous god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotten pulled into\Na real troublesome game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die either, but how\Nabout I give you half of my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for your thoughtfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never been in this to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would you like to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I been doing?\NI think I've used about two billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A shopping mall in that ghost town,\N500 containers for sea transport,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and entertainment expenses\Non the Foreign Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you seem to have done quite a bit else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I... kill a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't think I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You had some goal so important\Nyou erased your memory for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,judging from the logs, pre-amnesia\NNumber 9 was a pretty appealing guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you actually gave up your past\Nto place your bets on your new self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you should stay how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to meet you before I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, cut that out! You're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray you shall be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Juiz I owe you for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I've been able\Nto spend my money meaningfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense, I should apologize for\Nhow little I've been able to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've done plenty. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the Supporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared for this. I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supporter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Hiura, you're too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be satisfied until I punch out the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who forced this stupid phone on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future